    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to PyGObject3 Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>PyGObject3</application> provides
        <application>Python</application> bindings to the GObject
        class from <application>GLib</application>.
      </para>

      &lfs75_checked;

